room_title: Escape room "The Row" by Alcatraz Escape Games in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_address: 8800 N Tarrant Pkwy #200 North Richland Hills, TX 76182
room_description: You are being held on death row, agonizingly awaiting the electric chair. The prison has proven to be escape-proof, until now. Your contacts on the outside have placed a series of clues to aid in your escape. Use these clues wisely and you will problem-solve your way to freedom.
